
* Build documentation
- install Sphinx-doc : sudo apt-get install python-sphinx
- install the less compiler (requires node NPM) : sudo npm install -g less
- run 'make html' in doc/ directory

* Automated documentation building using the provided watcher :
- sudo aptitude install inotity-tools
  cd kasper-framework/doc
  ./watch.sh 

Refer to http://docutils.sourceforge.net/docs/user/rst/quickstart.html for reStructuredText format reference
Refer to http://sphinx-doc.org/contents.html for Sphinx documentation
